    javax.constraints
    This package describes a generic Java programming interface for Constraint Programming (CP API) - see www.jcp.org .

      Subinterfaces of Var in javax.constraints 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  VarBool
      This interface represents constrained boolean variables that can be seen as integer constrained variables with the domain { 0, 1 } but with a potentially more efficient implementation.
